'''League'''
* Most [[touchdown]]s returns in a season - (6) (2006, 2007)
* Most touchdowns kick and punt returns in a season - (6) (2007)
* Most touchdown returns as a rookie (6) - (2006)
* Most touchdown returns in one game (2)** - Against [[St. Louis Rams|St. Louis]] on [[December 11]], [[2006]] and [[Denver Broncos]] on [[November 25]], [[2007]]

'''Franchise'''
* Most regular season kick and punt returns (11)
* Most kickoff return yards in a game (225 yards) - Against St. Louis on December 11, 2006
* Most punt return yards in a game (152 yards) - Against [[Arizona Cardinals|Arizona]] on [[October 16]], [[2006]] 
* Most punt return yards in a season (651 yards) - 2007 season
* Longest play (108 yards)* - Against [[New York Giants]] on [[November 12]], [[2006]] 
<small>*Shared with [[Nathan Vasher]]<BR>**Shared with six others<BR></small>

